Note:
COBOL Lexer - Complete tokenization for COBOL/COBOL-85

Supports:
- All COBOL divisions (IDENTIFICATION, ENVIRONMENT, DATA, PROCEDURE)
- 100+ COBOL keywords (MOVE, ADD, COMPUTE, PERFORM, DISPLAY, ACCEPT, etc.)
- Picture clauses (PIC X, PIC 9, PIC S9V99, etc.)
- Level numbers (01-49, 66, 77, 88)
- Literals (numeric, alphanumeric with quotes or apostrophes)
- Figurative constants (ZERO, SPACES, HIGH-VALUES, LOW-VALUES, QUOTE, etc.)
- Comments (asterisk in column 7 or inline)
- Operators (arithmetic, relational, logical)
- Both fixed-format (column-sensitive) and free-format
- Period (.) as statement terminator

Token Types: 150+ distinct tokens for complete COBOL support
:End Note

Import "compiler/frontend/primitives/memory/layout.runa" as Layout
Import "compiler/frontend/primitives/core/string_core.runa" as StringCore

